OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FStaying
OL,6,Fmostly dry and mild overnight with
OL,7,Fvariable amounts of cloud and some
OL,8,Fclearer spells. Chance of some patchy
OL,9,Flight rain mainly across northern
OL,10,Fareas during the second half of the
OL,11,Fnight. Winds freshening a little.
OL,12,
OL,13,CThursday:FAny patchy rain or showers
OL,14,Fclearing southeast by late morning.
OL,15,FOtherwise remaining mainly fine with
OL,16,Fsome bright and sunny spells by the
OL,17,Fafternoon but becoming breezy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
