OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FFriday
OL,6,Fand into the weekend likely to remain
OL,7,Fdry and occasionally breezy, with some
OL,8,Fclear or sunny spells. Temperatures
OL,9,Fmostly above average throughout.
